    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-16a5ff81-d1c8-4a34-8fd5-f6ea5a03eb2a">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-16a5ff81-d1c8-4a34-8fd5-f6ea5a03eb2a">
                Mr. A. Henderson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-16a5ff81-d1c8-4a34-8fd5-f6ea5a03eb2a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-12-19/debates/40e0378d-5151-4cf4-9325-30cf258a6f3a/Nato(ParisConference)#contribution-16a5ff81-d1c8-4a34-8fd5-f6ea5a03eb2a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class=""><em>(by Private Notice)</em> asked the Prime Minister whether he has any statement to make on the meeting of Ministers of the North Atlantic Treaty Organisation Council, which met in Paris this week.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-16a5ff81-d1c8-4a34-8fd5-f6ea5a03eb2a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-12-19/debates/40e0378d-5151-4cf4-9325-30cf258a6f3a/Nato(ParisConference)#contribution-16a5ff81-d1c8-4a34-8fd5-f6ea5a03eb2a">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-8fae5aa3-4bb6-448b-8323-22a2fd177f0d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-8fae5aa3-4bb6-448b-8323-22a2fd177f0d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-8fae5aa3-4bb6-448b-8323-22a2fd177f0d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-8fae5aa3-4bb6-448b-8323-22a2fd177f0d">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8fae5aa3-4bb6-448b-8323-22a2fd177f0d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-12-19/debates/40e0378d-5151-4cf4-9325-30cf258a6f3a/Nato(ParisConference)#contribution-8fae5aa3-4bb6-448b-8323-22a2fd177f0d">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I have no further statement to make at this moment on the work of the Conference in Paris which would add to the very full reports and communiqués which have been published and to the statement which I made on the naval arrangements. If my right hon. Friend the Foreign Secretary had been here, he would have welcomed the opportunity of giving the House his personal impressions of what has been a most successful Conference. I regret to say, however, that he has been detained by an important business point which has arisen at the last minute, but which in no way alters the general conclusions in respect of the Conference.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8fae5aa3-4bb6-448b-8323-22a2fd177f0d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-12-19/debates/40e0378d-5151-4cf4-9325-30cf258a6f3a/Nato(ParisConference)#contribution-8fae5aa3-4bb6-448b-8323-22a2fd177f0d">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-2d8a1cfc-a3e5-4476-90b6-120bec516b93">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-2d8a1cfc-a3e5-4476-90b6-120bec516b93">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-2d8a1cfc-a3e5-4476-90b6-120bec516b93">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-2d8a1cfc-a3e5-4476-90b6-120bec516b93">
                Mr. Henderson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2d8a1cfc-a3e5-4476-90b6-120bec516b93" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-12-19/debates/40e0378d-5151-4cf4-9325-30cf258a6f3a/Nato(ParisConference)#contribution-2d8a1cfc-a3e5-4476-90b6-120bec516b93">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Has the Prime Minister's attention been drawn to the reported statement of General Ridgway to the effect that the 50 divisions which were the target for 1952 will be more like 35 divisions as a result of some of them being under-trained and under-equipped? Does the Prime Minister accept that statement? In any event, will he make it clear that the British divisions in N.A.T.O. are fully equipped and fully trained?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2d8a1cfc-a3e5-4476-90b6-120bec516b93" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-12-19/debates/40e0378d-5151-4cf4-9325-30cf258a6f3a/Nato(ParisConference)#contribution-2d8a1cfc-a3e5-4476-90b6-120bec516b93">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-37ac1d39-d429-4915-8303-d665026812b1">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-37ac1d39-d429-4915-8303-d665026812b1">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-37ac1d39-d429-4915-8303-d665026812b1">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-37ac1d39-d429-4915-8303-d665026812b1">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-37ac1d39-d429-4915-8303-d665026812b1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-12-19/debates/40e0378d-5151-4cf4-9325-30cf258a6f3a/Nato(ParisConference)#contribution-37ac1d39-d429-4915-8303-d665026812b1">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As to the last part of the question, I can certainly give that assurance. As to the more general issues involved, it is quite clear that these matters have to be fully discussed when we meet again, but certainly no justice could be done to topics of such wide scope and variegated character in the closing hours of the Session.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-37ac1d39-d429-4915-8303-d665026812b1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-12-19/debates/40e0378d-5151-4cf4-9325-30cf258a6f3a/Nato(ParisConference)#contribution-37ac1d39-d429-4915-8303-d665026812b1">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
